The Zines

In August and September 2024 I’m focussing on scanning the covers and adding them to the database so we can get a sense of the whole archive. I’ll then return to full scanning which I estimate will take about three years?

Thumbnails link to archive pages for each publication. Metadata is pretty basic on this first pass. I will go back and add all contributors over the next year. The zines are now sorted by title and you can filter by type or country.

Publisher and contributor names are linked. Most of these will work. Some won’t! Sorry if yours doesn’t yet…

Full search to come later.

1649 zines of the approx 4-5,000 in the archive have been processed with more added every few days. Last updated 04 Sep 2024

A log of updates can be found here, also available as an RSS feed.

Type: Zines | Review Zines | Comics | Anthology Comics | Other
Country: UK | USA | RoW

Comics comprise the majority of zines in this archive because those were the communities I was involved with. As such it’s an unweildy category in need of breaking down but for now it comprises publications that are analogous to a comic book or graphic novel, usually containing a main story and anchored by one or two people. Some will have zine-y features, such as articles, inteviews, letters and reviews, while others will have just the story between covers. Some will be serialised over many issues, other stand alone. Contrast with Anthology comics.
